text.tspan: STEP ONE : MEASURE
Metabolic:
this section provides you with useful information about your risk for:
obesity, diabetes, male-pattern baldness, lactose intolerance, and enzymes that
are involved in toxin detoxication (Both phase I and Phase II).
Heart:
this section includes a highly actionable assessment of your risk for: heart
attack, coronary artery disease (CAD), high blood pressure, atrial brillation, and
preventable causes of sudden cardiac death. In addition, this section provides a full
analysis of how your body is likely to respond to common cardiovascular medications.
Blood:
A genetic assessment of your risk for: blood clots such as deep
vein thrombosis (DVTS), abnormal bleeding, hemochromatosis, elevated
Homocysteine levels that are reversible with B-vitamin supplementation and
hypersensitivity to lead and other environmental toxins.
Brain:
focused on keeping your brain healthy throughout your life. This section
pr
ovides you with essential information to help protect you from: Alzheimers
disease, dementia risk following head trauma, stroke, brain aneurysms, and
macular degeneration.
Cancer:
a genetic assessment of preventable cancers including your risk of: skin cancer,
colon cancer, prostate cancer, breast cancer and cancer due to sensitivity to radiation.
Included in this section is also an assessment of your risk for rare cancers including a
number of cancer syndromes (such as Lynch syndrome) and cancer of the adrenal glands.
Nutrition and Fitness:
a genetic assessment tells of your risk for osteopenia,
osteoporosis and arthritis. You will also be provided with a genetically tailored
tness regime to prevent bone disease and optimize your time at the gym.
Eternitys Predictive Medicine Genetic Testing Panel provides the worlds most comprehensive assessment of your genes.
All diseases and conditions assessed are preventable, making this information highly actionable. Your genetic information will
be conveyed in an easy to understand genetic report that is focused on empowering you and your healthcare provider with
personal solutions for better health. Utilizing the unique information contained within your genes, you and your doctor will
be able to focus on preventing disease before it occurs, allowing you to enhance your health and longevity. (Eternity strongly
recommends you obtain this test)
